</div>

<div class="progreso-contenedor">
  <i class="fas fa-eye fa-2x" style="color: #ffd600;"></i>
  <div class="puntos" id="puntosProgreso">
    <div class="punto activo">1</div>
    <div class="punto">2</div>
    <div class="punto">3</div>
    <div class="punto">4</div>
  </div>
  <span class="badge" style="background: #ffd600; color: #0d47a1; padding: 8px 20px;">P&aacute;gina <span id="paginaActualNum">1</span>/4</span>
</div>

<div class="contenedor">

  <div class="pagina activa" id="pagina1">
    <div class="tarjeta-visual">
      <h2 class="titulo-pagina"><i class="fas fa-sync-alt me-3"></i> ROTACI&Oacute;N</h2>

      <div class="grid-2cols">
        <div class="imagen-grande" onclick="ampliarImagen(this.querySelector('img'))">
          <img src="/contenidos/geografia/recursos/imagenes/libro/rotacion-tierra.jpg"
               alt="Rotaci&oacute;n" class="imagen-geo"
               onerror="this.src='https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9d/Earth_rotation.svg/800px-Earth_rotation.svg.png'">
          <div class="pie-imagen">&#127757; Gira sobre su propio eje</div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="contenedor-horas">
            <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
            <h4>24 HORAS</h4>
            <p>Duraci&oacute;n de la rotaci&oacute;n</p>
          </div>
          <div class="fila-doble">
            <div class="caja-info">
              <i class="fas fa-sun"></i>
              <h4>D&Iacute;A</h4>
              <p>Frente al Sol</p>
            </div>
            <div class="caja-info">
              <i class="fas fa-moon"></i>
              <h4>NOCHE</h4>
              <p>Espaldas al Sol</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-4">
        <span class="etiqueta">&#11014; Gira de Oeste a Este &middot; El Sol sale por el Este</span>
      </div>

      <div class="reforzamiento">
        <div class="reforzamiento-titulo"><i class="fas fa-hand-pointer"></i> Responde</div>
        <p class="reforzamiento-instruccion">
          Los tres relojes muestran distintas duraciones. Haz clic en el que indica cu&aacute;nto tarda la Tierra en completar una rotaci&oacute;n completa.
        </p>
        <div class="opciones-svg">

          <div class="opcion-svg" id="r1A" onclick="responder1('A')">
            <svg width="140" height="160" viewBox="0 0 140 160">
              <rect width="140" height="160" fill="#283593" rx="18"/>
              <circle cx="70" cy="78" r="52" fill="#1a3a6e" stroke="#4a6fa5" stroke-width="3"/>
              <line x1="70" y1="30" x2="70" y2="38" stroke="#7a9cc5" stroke-width="2.5"/>
              <line x1="70" y1="118" x2="70" y2="126" stroke="#7a9cc5" stroke-width="2.5"/>
              <line x1="22" y1="78" x2="30" y2="78" stroke="#7a9cc5" stroke-width="2.5"/>
              <line x1="110" y1="78" x2="118" y2="78" stroke="#7a9cc5" stroke-width="2.5"/>
              <line x1="70" y1="78" x2="70" y2="36" stroke="#b3c5f7" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="70" y1="78" x2="70" y2="110" stroke="#ffd600" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <circle cx="70" cy="78" r="4" fill="#b3c5f7"/>
            </svg>
            <span>12 horas</span>
          </div>

          <div class="opcion-svg" id="r1B" onclick="responder1('B')">
            <svg width="140" height="160" viewBox="0 0 140 160">
              <rect width="140" height="160" fill="#283593" rx="18"/>
              <circle cx="70" cy="78" r="52" fill="#1a3a6e" stroke="#4a6fa5" stroke-width="3"/>
              <line x1="70" y1="30" x2="70" y2="38" stroke="#7a9cc5" stroke-width="2.5"/>
              <line x1="70" y1="118" x2="70" y2="126" stroke="#7a9cc5" stroke-width="2.5"/>
              <line x1="22" y1="78" x2="30" y2="78" stroke="#7a9cc5" stroke-width="2.5"/>
              <line x1="110" y1="78" x2="118" y2="78" stroke="#7a9cc5" stroke-width="2.5"/>
              <line x1="70" y1="78" x2="70" y2="36" stroke="#b3c5f7" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="70" y1="78" x2="70" y2="36" stroke="#ffd600" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M 70 33 A 45 45 0 1 1 69 33" fill="none" stroke="#ffd600" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-dasharray="6,4" opacity="0.6"/>
              <polygon points="69,26 65,34 73,34" fill="#ffd600" opacity="0.7"/>
              <circle cx="70" cy="78" r="4" fill="#b3c5f7"/>
            </svg>
            <span>24 horas</span>
          </div>

          <div class="opcion-svg" id="r1C" onclick="responder1('C')">
            <svg width="140" height="160" viewBox="0 0 140 160">
              <rect width="140" height="160" fill="#283593" rx="18"/>
              <circle cx="70" cy="78" r="52" fill="#1a3a6e" stroke="#4a6fa5" stroke-width="3"/>
              <line x1="70" y1="30" x2="70" y2="38" stroke="#7a9cc5" stroke-width="2.5"/>
              <line x1="70" y1="118" x2="70" y2="126" stroke="#7a9cc5" stroke-width="2.5"/>
              <line x1="22" y1="78" x2="30" y2="78" stroke="#7a9cc5" stroke-width="2.5"/>
              <line x1="110" y1="78" x2="118" y2="78" stroke="#7a9cc5" stroke-width="2.5"/>
              <line x1="70" y1="78" x2="70" y2="36" stroke="#b3c5f7" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="70" y1="78" x2="96" y2="52" stroke="#ffd600" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <circle cx="70" cy="78" r="4" fill="#b3c5f7"/>
              <text x="70" y="82" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Fredoka One" font-size="13" fill="#ffd600">365d</text>
            </svg>
            <span>365 d&iacute;as</span>
          </div>

        </div>
        <div class="feedback-ref" id="fb1"></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="pagina" id="pagina2">
    <div class="tarjeta-visual">
      <h2 class="titulo-pagina"><i class="fas fa-orbit me-3"></i> TRASLACI&Oacute;N</h2>

      <div class="grid-2cols">
        <div class="imagen-grande" onclick="ampliarImagen(this.querySelector('img'))">
          <img src="/contenidos/geografia/recursos/imagenes/libro/traslacion-tierra.jpg"
               alt="Traslaci&oacute;n" class="imagen-geo"
               onerror="this.src='https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/94/Earth_orbit.svg/800px-Earth_orbit.svg.png'">
          <div class="pie-imagen">&#9728; Orbita alrededor del Sol</div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="contenedor-horas mb-3">
            <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i>
            <h4>365 D&Iacute;AS</h4>
            <p>+ 6 horas cada a&ntilde;o</p>
          </div>
          <div class="contenedor-horas">
            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
            <h4>A&Ntilde;O BISIESTO</h4>
            <p>Cada 4 a&ntilde;os &middot; Febrero 29</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-4">
        <span class="etiqueta">&#128640; Velocidad: 107,000 km/h</span>
      </div>

      <div class="reforzamiento">
        <div class="reforzamiento-titulo"><i class="fas fa-hand-pointer"></i> Responde</div>
        <p class="reforzamiento-instruccion">
          Cada calendario muestra cada cu&aacute;ntos a&ntilde;os ocurre el a&ntilde;o bisiesto. Haz clic en el correcto.
        </p>
        <div class="opciones-svg">

          <div class="opcion-svg" id="r2A" onclick="responder2('A')">
            <svg width="140" height="160" viewBox="0 0 140 160">
              <rect width="140" height="160" fill="#283593" rx="18"/>
              <rect x="10" y="10" width="120" height="30" rx="8" fill="#4a6fa5"/>
              <text x="70" y="30" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Fredoka One" font-size="15" fill="#ffd600">Bisiesto</text>
              <rect x="10" y="45" width="120" height="104" rx="8" fill="#1a3a6e"/>
              <text x="70" y="115" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Fredoka One" font-size="62" fill="#4a6fa5">2</text>
              <text x="70" y="140" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#7a9cc5">a&ntilde;os</text>
              <rect x="42" y="6" width="10" height="16" rx="5" fill="#4a6fa5"/>
              <rect x="88" y="6" width="10" height="16" rx="5" fill="#4a6fa5"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Cada 2 a&ntilde;os</span>
          </div>

          <div class="opcion-svg" id="r2B" onclick="responder2('B')">
            <svg width="140" height="160" viewBox="0 0 140 160">
              <rect width="140" height="160" fill="#283593" rx="18"/>
              <rect x="10" y="10" width="120" height="30" rx="8" fill="#4a6fa5"/>
              <text x="70" y="30" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Fredoka One" font-size="15" fill="#ffd600">Bisiesto</text>
              <rect x="10" y="45" width="120" height="104" rx="8" fill="#1a3a6e"/>
              <text x="70" y="115" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Fredoka One" font-size="62" fill="#4a6fa5">4</text>
              <text x="70" y="140" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#7a9cc5">a&ntilde;os</text>
              <rect x="42" y="6" width="10" height="16" rx="5" fill="#4a6fa5"/>
              <rect x="88" y="6" width="10" height="16" rx="5" fill="#4a6fa5"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Cada 4 a&ntilde;os</span>
          </div>

          <div class="opcion-svg" id="r2C" onclick="responder2('C')">
            <svg width="140" height="160" viewBox="0 0 140 160">
              <rect width="140" height="160" fill="#283593" rx="18"/>
              <rect x="10" y="10" width="120" height="30" rx="8" fill="#4a6fa5"/>
              <text x="70" y="30" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Fredoka One" font-size="15" fill="#ffd600">Bisiesto</text>
              <rect x="10" y="45" width="120" height="104" rx="8" fill="#1a3a6e"/>
              <text x="70" y="115" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Fredoka One" font-size="52" fill="#4a6fa5">10</text>
              <text x="70" y="140" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Nunito" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#7a9cc5">a&ntilde;os</text>
              <rect x="42" y="6" width="10" height="16" rx="5" fill="#4a6fa5"/>
              <rect x="88" y="6" width="10" height="16" rx="5" fill="#4a6fa5"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Cada 10 a&ntilde;os</span>
          </div>

        </div>
        <div class="feedback-ref" id="fb2"></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="pagina" id="pagina3">
    <div class="tarjeta-visual">
      <h2 class="titulo-pagina"><i class="fas fa-seedling me-3"></i> ESTACIONES</h2>

      <div class="imagen-grande mb-4" onclick="ampliarImagen(this.querySelector('img'))">
        <img src="/contenidos/geografia/recursos/imagenes/libro/estaciones.jpg"
             alt="Estaciones" class="imagen-geo"
             onerror="this.src='https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8b/Seasons.svg/800px-Seasons.svg.png'">
        <div class="pie-imagen">&#127777; Las 4 estaciones</div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-4cols">
        <div class="estacion-card">
          <i class="fas fa-seedling"></i>
          <h5>PRIMAVERA</h5>
          <p>21 Mar - 20 Jun</p>
        </div>
        <div class="estacion-card">
          <i class="fas fa-sun"></i>
          <h5>VERANO</h5>
          <p>21 Jun - 22 Sep</p>
        </div>
        <div class="estacion-card">
          <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
          <h5>OTO&Ntilde;O</h5>
          <p>23 Sep - 20 Dic</p>
        </div>
        <div class="estacion-card">
          <i class="fas fa-snowflake"></i>
          <h5>INVIERNO</h5>
          <p>21 Dic - 20 Mar</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="caja-info mt-4">
        <i class="fas fa-globe-americas"></i>
        <h4>HEMISFERIOS OPUESTOS</h4>
        <p class="fs-5">&#127474;&#127485; Norte &rarr; Verano &middot; &#127462;&#127479; Sur &rarr; Invierno</p>
      </div>

      <div class="reforzamiento">
        <div class="reforzamiento-titulo"><i class="fas fa-hand-pointer"></i> Responde</div>
        <p class="reforzamiento-instruccion">
          Cuando en M&eacute;xico (Hemisferio Norte) es verano, haz clic en el hemisferio del globo donde es invierno al mismo tiempo.
